Suzanne Whang https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzanne_Whang 0 Suzanne Whang is an American television host, actress, comedian, radio host, published author, minister, writer, producer, and political activist. She is best known as the former host of the HGTV series House Hunters for nine years, and for her recurring role as manicurist Polly Chae on Las Vegas for four seasons. Suzanne is currently starring as Divina the maid / wannabe actress in the Here TV sitcom From Here on OUT.
